inoremap jk <esc>
" Capitalize word
inoremap <c-u> <esc>viwUwa
" Fully un-capitalize word
inoremap <c-l> <esc>viwuwa
inoremap <c-d> <esc>^Di
" Create open / close tags with current word
inoremap <c-t><c-i> <esc>bviwdi<</<esc>pa><esc>Bpa><esc>i
